# GANG Platform Standards Index

This document serves as the master index for all platform standards, rules, and quality bars.

## Core Principles

1. **Documents, not apps** - Static HTML + CSS; no JS on read-only pages
2. **Enforce budgets** - HTML ≤30KB, CSS ≤10KB, JS=0 on content
3. **WCAG 2.2 AA compliance** - Accessibility is non-negotiable
4. **Performance targets** - Lighthouse ≥95/98/100/100

