## Build Requirements

### Performance Budgets (per page)
- HTML: ≤30KB
- CSS: ≤10KB
- JS: 0 on content pages (posts, pages, projects, newsletters)
- JS: ≤10KB on interactive pages (products, cart)
- Images: ≤500KB total per page

### Lighthouse Thresholds
- Performance: ≥95
- Accessibility: ≥98
- Best Practices: 100
- SEO: 100

### Required Elements (Every Page)
- Exactly one `<h1>`
- Semantic landmarks: `header`, `main`, `footer`
- JSON-LD structured data
- Canonical URL
- Meta description
- Open Graph tags
- Alt text on all images

## Quality Gates

All builds must pass:
1. ✅ Slug uniqueness check
2. ✅ Content quality score ≥85
3. ✅ WCAG AA compliance (axe)
4. ✅ Lighthouse assertions
5. ✅ Valid HTML (Nu validator)
6. ✅ Link validation (no 404s)

## Contract Enforcement

See `/contracts/*.yml` for page-type specific contracts defining:
- Required headings structure
- Landmark requirements
- JSON-LD properties
- Byte budgets
- Accessibility requirements

